  <!-- EN: Quest expired: [resolvedQuestName] -->
  <VFE_OpportunitySite_AbandonedFactory.LetterLabelQuestExpired.slateRef>クエストの期限切れ：[resolvedQuestName]</VFE_OpportunitySite_AbandonedFactory.LetterLabelQuestExpired.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: The bandit camp has packed up and moved on. The quest [resolvedQuestName] has expired. -->
  <VFE_OpportunitySite_AbandonedFactory.LetterTextQuestExpired.slateRef>山賊キャンプは準備が整って,移動しました.クエスト[resolvedQuestName]は期限切れです.</VFE_OpportunitySite_AbandonedFactory.LetterTextQuestExpired.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: Quest failed: [resolvedQuestName] -->
  <VFE_OpportunitySite_AbandonedFactory.LetterLabelQuestFailed.slateRef>クエスト失敗：[resolvedQuestName]</VFE_OpportunitySite_AbandonedFactory.LetterLabelQuestFailed.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: After being discovered, the bandit camp has dispersed. The quest [resolvedQuestName] has ended. -->
  <VFE_OpportunitySite_AbandonedFactory.LetterTextQuestFailed.slateRef>クエスト終了：[resolvedQuestName]\n発見された後,山賊キャンプは移動しました.</VFE_OpportunitySite_AbandonedFactory.LetterTextQuestFailed.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: Payment arrived -->
  <VFE_OpportunitySite_AbandonedFactory.LetterLabelPaymentArrived.slateRef>報酬が届いた</VFE_OpportunitySite_AbandonedFactory.LetterLabelPaymentArrived.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: You have defeated the bandit camp!\n\nThe payment from [asker_faction_name] has arrived. -->
  <VFE_OpportunitySite_AbandonedFactory.LetterTextPaymentArrived.slateRef>山賊キャンプを討伐しました！\n\n[asker_faction_name]からの報酬が届きました.</VFE_OpportunitySite_AbandonedFactory.LetterTextPaymentArrived.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: [asker_faction_royalFavorLabel] -->
  <VFE_OpportunitySite_AbandonedFactory.LetterLabelFavorReceiver.slateRef>[asker_faction_royalFavorLabel]</VFE_OpportunitySite_AbandonedFactory.LetterLabelFavorReceiver.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: These colonists participated in the victory for the quest [resolvedQuestName]. [asker_definite] wants to know who should receive the [royalFavorReward_amount] [asker_faction_royalFavorLabel] for this service. -->
  <VFE_OpportunitySite_AbandonedFactory.LetterTextFavorReceiver.slateRef>これらの入植者たちは,[resolvedQuestName]探索の戦いと勝利に参加しました.[asker_definite]は,このクエスト報酬として[royalFavorReward_amount][asker_faction_royalFavorLabel]を誰が受けとるのか知りたがっています.</VFE_OpportunitySite_AbandonedFactory.LetterTextFavorReceiver.slateRef>

